    "description": "Join the battle between two peasant kingdoms and utilize whatever means necessary to ensure victory! Define your playstyle by mastering the in-depth <u>2D hand-to-hand combat</u> mechanics, <u>building vehicles</u> with high firepower, or by <u>casting powerful magic spells</u> from the backline for a more supportive role. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/26ed3c4ef9bbaa4a4e6905babd14ab2f.avif?t=1761860757\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br>Take control of your personal magic wand -companion to quickly construct castles and vehicles. You can make everything from small agile contraptions to humongous air-bases. Attach weaponry and other useful items to create mobile war machines capable of quickly getting friendly peasants into combat and delivering destruction from above.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/077ecd0f752e0f3cd029c6e33339c369.poster.avif?t=1761860757\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/077ecd0f752e0f3cd029c6e33339c369.webm?t=1761860757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/077ecd0f752e0f3cd029c6e33339c369.mp4?t=1761860757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/9cf04b4f7e824244a5b696afd48d940e.avif?t=1761860757\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br>Everything is destructible! Collapse big castles, dig tunnels, burn houses, and blow up vehicles by using magic spells and other tools at your disposal. Flying vehicles with enough momentum are also an excellent source of destruction, but remember to make them sturdy enough!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/be32ea0f144ac2912c2e44e909678a5f.poster.avif?t=1761860757\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/be32ea0f144ac2912c2e44e909678a5f.webm?t=1761860757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/be32ea0f144ac2912c2e44e909678a5f.mp4?t=1761860757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/64fbe46d45b942d2b8cbd3de50f2e19d.avif?t=1761860757\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br>Select a combination of weapons that fit your combat style the best! You can dual wield swords or even shields if feeling extra defensive. Each weapon has its own unique ability that synergizes with other abilities. Peasants also have access to one wildcard ability of their choosing, and a generic purpose kick to use in various ways such as nudging vehicles and parrying attacks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/7fb4e6092e8934e9ef3b2ceef39cfb6f.poster.avif?t=1761860757\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/7fb4e6092e8934e9ef3b2ceef39cfb6f.webm?t=1761860757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/7fb4e6092e8934e9ef3b2ceef39cfb6f.mp4?t=1761860757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/6cbfd71ebbae866fb4e6faf3fb64ec99.avif?t=1761860757\" width=616 height=80 /></span><br>Use your magic wand to cast powerful spells varying from lingering area-of-effect zones to controllable projectiles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/049045ed4c397be875494be79820cd9f.poster.avif?t=1761860757\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/049045ed4c397be875494be79820cd9f.webm?t=1761860757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3014500/extras/049045ed4c397be875494be79820cd9f.mp4?t=1761860757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
